title: A Look Back at the ‘Real World’ With Juliet Litman | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny joined Juliet Litman on ‘Ringer Dish’ to discuss the legacy of the ‘Real World’ and why the ‘Real World: Homecoming’ series on Paramount+ is so successful.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Juliet Litman
Producers: Devon Manze, Chelsea Stark-Jones, and Sasha Ashall
